en:
You don't remember?
Well, I understand since we never directly
spoke to each other before.

My name is <c=pistachio>Olive</c>.
I'm <c=pistachio>Pistachio</c>'s older sister!

I heard that you guys tried to prevent the
crystals from being stolen...
but <c=violastro>that thief</c> got away, didn't he?

I wanted to check up on <c=pistachio>my little sister</c>, but
instead I ran into <c=131,42,13>Hickory</c> who told me what
had happened.

I'm glad you are all okay.
I don't know what I'd do if something were to
happen to <c=pistachio>my little sister</c>...
Please be careful on your adventures!
